        <h1>Instructions</h1>
      <ol>
        <li>The entire game comprises of various levels starting with level 0 and there are total 10 territories. </li>
        <li>Level 0  has  ___ territories unlocked and you can choose to attack any territory among them. And after conquering level 0  territories your way to further level territories will be unlocked.</li>
        <li>Initially, you are given with 500 troops, and you have to find a suitable territory to attack ; the territory whose minimum troops requirement is satisfied.</li>
        <li>In order to gain control over the territory you need to solve a coding ques popped on your screen as you clicked on the desired territory.</li>
        <li>If you correctly answer the question , your army size increases by ___ of total army of that country.</li>
        <li>In case you fail to do so, your army size will decrease by 100 of your current army.</li>
        <li>Also, you will be provided with 3 bonus questions throughout the game.</li>
        <li>Correctly answering the bonus question will increase your army size by ____ , whereas answering incorrectly will decrease your army size by ____.</li>
        <li>And before starting, remember the winning criteria is maximum number of territories conquered and size of army.</li>
